rows.label: tev001893_MSG0001
rows.name: Ch-Chief![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0002
rows.name: Guess the cat's outta the bag, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_JNK0010
rows.name: Interrogate

rows.label: tev001893_SEL0011
rows.name: Demand to know if Mia killed those men.

rows.label: tev001893_JNK0020
rows.name: Worry

rows.label: tev001893_SEL0021
rows.name: Make sure that Mia is not hurt.

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0003
rows.name:
Killed? No! Not really. Just taught 'em a little lesson.
Their mimeosomes are a lot tougher than they look.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0004
rows.name:
Don't worry about me. I'm a full-fledged BLADE who
was trained by the best! By which I mean you, Chief.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0005
rows.name:
I guess I can tell you what happened now.
I've been on a deep-cover operation.
Super cloak-and-dagger-type stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0006
rows.name:
And the client was Sakuraba Industries themselves!
They wanted me to snare some group who was trying
to steal information about their new weapon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0007
rows.name:
If the information had leaked to a rival company—
or worse, one of our enemies—it would have been
a really bad scene.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0008
rows.name:
We were having our first meeting about the job when
you ran into me that night in the residential district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0009
rows.name:
And when you saw me in the commercial district,
that was when they were having me steal the intel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0010
rows.name:
The intel was fake, of course. Just some sham to give
to the group that was trying to steal it for reals.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0011
rows.name:
And today was the day I sprung the trap and arrested
the conspirators![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0012
rows.name: So what do you think? Preeetty neat, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_JNK0030
rows.name: Praise

rows.label: tev001893_SEL0031
rows.name:
Say that her plan seems to have
been executed flawlessly.

rows.label: tev001893_JNK0040
rows.name: Tease

rows.label: tev001893_SEL0041
rows.name:
Joke that only Mia would come up
with something this complicated.

rows.label: tev001893_JNK0050
rows.name: Bluff

rows.label: tev001893_SEL0051
rows.name: Claim that you had it figured out from the start.

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0013
rows.name: Aw! Thanks, Chief![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0014
rows.name:
I had a lot of support from Sakuraba Industries,
but I'm still pretty pumped that I was able to capture
the criminals all by myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0015
rows.name: This mission has really given me a lot of confidence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0016
rows.name:
I'm gonna keep taking harder and harder missions,
and before you know it, you'll have a new rival on
your hands! A RIVAL! So cool.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0017
rows.name:
Except that YOUR constant interference almost blew the
whole darn thing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0018
rows.name:
But thankfully my expert improvisation saved the day
and brought the mission to a flawless end.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0019
rows.name:
Also, doing it all by myself really helped to boost my
confidence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0020
rows.name:
I'm gonna keep taking harder and harder missions,
and before you know it, you'll have a new rival on
your hands! A RIVAL! So cool.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0021
rows.name:
You are so full of it, Chief. You're like a silo!
Or...some other building that's full of stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0022
rows.name:
I guess I've grown so much as a BLADE that even you
can't believe it, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0023
rows.name:
Although I must admit that I DID have a lot of support
from Sakuraba Industries this time around.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001893_MSG0024
rows.name:
Still, I'm gonna keep taking harder missions,
and before you know it, you'll have a new rival on
your hands! A RIVAL! So cool.[ST:wait ]
